      *                  * Test se differenza tra totali generali in   *
      *                  * termini di valore inevaso                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tot-gen-tvi        not  = w-tot-gen-tvo
                     go to prn-fin-cic-020.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da stampare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tot-gen-cli        not  > 1
                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
       prn-fin-cic-020.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
