      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se interruzione forzata : uscita        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salto interlinea vuota                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-fin-cic-200.
       prn-fin-cic-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
