      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Interlinea                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Stampa                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
