      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-prn-ini-lr2-ctr      .
           inspect   w-prn-ini-lr2-x63    
                                      tallying w-prn-ini-lr2-ctr
                                          for  trailing spaces        .
           subtract  w-prn-ini-lr2-ctr    from 63
                                        giving w-prn-ini-lr2-pnt      .
